The paper deals with power control for streaming variable bit rate (VBR) videos over wireless links, which is a problem related to networked systems and multimedia. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.MM (Multimedia) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization techniques and machine learning algorithms, which suggest that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
